WEBVTT

00:02.383 --> 00:04.383
Did you hear about this study
that found people

00:04.385 --> 00:06.986
that were cool and popular
at 13

00:06.988 --> 00:08.721
have problems succeeding
later in life?

00:08.723 --> 00:11.157
Hmm. I'm doing okay,
and I was very popular at 13.

00:11.159 --> 00:12.291
In school?

00:12.293 --> 00:13.959
Oh, no. At home.

00:14.729 --> 00:15.928
The servants would sing to me,

00:15.930 --> 00:17.830
laugh at my jokes...

00:18.633 --> 00:22.134
I wish I knew their names.

00:22.136 --> 00:25.104
Does the study say what happens
to the unpopular kids?

00:25.106 --> 00:27.573
You tell me-- you woke up
in bed with one.

00:28.709 --> 00:30.543
Listen to this.

00:30.545 --> 00:33.245
I just received an e-mail
from Wil Wheaton.

00:33.247 --> 00:36.248
Leonard Nimoy's son is
working on a documentary

00:36.250 --> 00:38.517
that he started with his
father before he passed away.

00:38.519 --> 00:40.719
It's about Mr. Spock and
his impact on our culture.

00:40.721 --> 00:41.687
Hmm.

00:41.689 --> 00:42.922
Why is he writing to you?

00:42.924 --> 00:44.924
Well, they're looking
for fans to interview,

00:44.926 --> 00:46.692
and Wil thought
I'd be good for it.

00:46.694 --> 00:47.760
Oh. Hey, high five.

00:47.762 --> 00:49.161
Absolutely not.

00:50.798 --> 00:51.764
Yeah, Penny,

00:51.766 --> 00:52.932
you spent some time
in front

00:52.934 --> 00:55.267
of the camera.
Any words of advice?

00:55.269 --> 00:56.569
Yes. Don't take your shirt off

00:56.571 --> 00:58.971
just because the director
said so.

00:58.973 --> 01:01.207
This is a documentary
about Mr. Spock.

01:01.209 --> 01:04.677
I'm sure if there's nudity,
it will be tasteful.

01:05.746 --> 01:09.381
♪ Our whole universe
was in a hot, dense state ♪

01:09.383 --> 01:12.718
♪ Then nearly 14 billion years
ago expansion started... Wait! ♪

01:12.720 --> 01:14.353
♪ The Earth began to cool ♪

01:14.355 --> 01:16.889
♪ The autotrophs began to drool,
Neanderthals developed tools ♪

01:16.891 --> 01:19.558
♪ We built the Wall ♪
♪<i> We built the pyramids</i> ♪

01:19.560 --> 01:22.228
♪ Math, Science, History,
unraveling the mystery ♪

01:22.230 --> 01:24.129
♪ That all started
with a big bang ♪

01:24.131 --> 01:26.098
♪<i> Bang!</i> ♪

